  "about": {
    "heroTitle": "Ibyerekeye AmataLink",
    "heroSubtitle": "Guha ubushobozi abahinzi n'abakusanyi b'amata mu Rwanda binyuze mu mishinga y'ikoranabuhanga",
    "missionTitle": "Inshingano Zacu",
    "missionDesc": "Gushyira mu ikoranabuhanga no kuringaniza urukurikirane rw'amata mu cyaro cy'u Rwanda, hizezwa umucyo, ukuri, n'inyungu ikwiye kuri bose. Tugamije gusimbuza uburyo bw'impapuro n'uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga bworoheye buri wese buha ubushobozi abahinzi n'abakusanyi.",
    "visionTitle": "Icyerekezo Cyacu",
    "visionDesc": "Kuba uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga buza imbere mu gucunga umusaruro w'amata muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba, guteza imbere iterambere rirambye mu nganda z'amata binyuze mu buhanga. Twifuza igihe kizaza aho buri muhinzi w'amata agira uburyo bwo gukurikirana umusaruro we n'inyungu ze ku gihe.",
    "storyTitle": "Amateka Yacu",
    "storyDesc1": "AmataLink yavutse imaze kubona imbogamizi abahinzi b'amata bahura nazo mu cyaro cy'u Rwanda. Uburyo bwa kera bw'impapuro bwatezaga amakimbirane, kubura amakuru, no gutinda kwishyurwa.",
    "storyDesc2": "Muri 2025, washinze uyu mushinga, Sarah Mukamana, wahoze ari umukusanyi ku mudugudu, yafashe icyemezo cyo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga mu gukemura ibi bibazo. Hamwe n'itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'ikoranabuhanga n'ubuhinzi, twakoze AmataLink - uburyo bworoshye kandi bugera kuri bose bwagenewe umuryango w'aborozi mu Rwanda.",
    "storyDesc3": "Uyu munsi, dukorana n'abahinzi barenga 100 mu midugudu itandukanye, tukanandika amalitiro ibihumbi buri munsi kandi tukizera gukurikirana amata ku buryo bw'umucyo kuva ku muhinzi kugeza ku kigo gikurikirana.",
    "valuesTitle": "Indangagaciro Zacu",
    "valuesSubtitle": "Amahame atuyobora mu byo dukora byose",
    "value1Title": "Umucyo",
    "value1Desc": "Twizera itumanaho risobanutse kandi rirangwa n'ubunyangamugayo n'abafatanyabikorwa bose.",
    "value2Title": "Guhanga Udushya",
    "value2Desc": "Gukoresha ikoranabuhanga mu gukemura imbogamizi nyazo abahinzi n'abakusanyi bahura nazo.",
    "value3Title": "Ubufatanye",
    "value3Desc": "Wubaka ubufatanye hagati y'abahinzi, abakusanyi, n'abayobozi kugirango bose bagere ku ntego.",
